        Parent:=PuTTYPage.Surface;
        Caption:=
            'This uses plink.exe from the PuTTY package which needs to be' + #13 +
            'provided by the user. The GIT_SSH environment variable will be' + #13 +
            'set to the path to plink.exe as specified below.';
